        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued August 6 at 5:15PM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>At 514 PM MDT, Doppler radar was tracking virga showers along a line
extending from 9 miles south of Avondale to 7 miles west of Tyrone.
Movement was east at 40 mph.

HAZARD...Wind gusts of 50 to 55 mph.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Gusty winds could knock down tree limbs and blow around
unsecured objects.

Locations impacted include...
Fowler, Delhi, Thatcher, and Tyrone.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
